com.foreach.across.core.context

Class ModuleConfigurationSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.core.context.ModuleConfigurationSet

  • public class ModuleConfigurationSet
extends Object
    Represents a collection of - usually @ModuleConfiguration - classes, mapped on the module names they apply for. These classes will be registered in the module using an ImportSelector in order to ensure correct conditional validation without premature class-loading. As such, only Configuration annotated classes are correctly handled.
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    ClassPathScanningModuleConfigurationProvider, ModuleConfigurationExtension
